âœ… Why These Are Perfect for Java 8 Stream Practice
â€¢	They force use of core Stream APIs: map, filter, flatMap, collect, groupingBy, counting, sorted, distinct, reduce, peek, limit, skip, etc.
â€¢	Many problems benefit from Collectors.groupingBy + Collectors.counting combo.
â€¢	Several problems can be solved without loops using IntStream.range + substring logic.
â€¢	Great for showing functional programming fluency in Java during interviews.
